### Problem07


Suppose that the following 31 keys appear (in some order) in a BST of height 4:

10 15 18 21 23 24 30 31 38 41 42 45 50 55 59 60 61 63 71 77 78 83 84 85 86 88 91 92 93 94 98

Draw the top three nodes of the tree (the root and its two children).  
Top three:  
Root node: _____(0)\___  
Left children node: _____(1)\___  
Right children node: _____(2)\___
question_content.author: Yantao Mei
